OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening and night. Rather cloudy,
OL,7,Fespecially in the east, while the west
OL,8,Fwill see more in the way of clearer
OL,9,Fspells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FDry and bright but rather
OL,12,Fcloudy, with the best chance of
OL,13,Fsunnier spells in the west and
OL,14,Fdeveloping during the afternoon.
OL,15,FWarmer in the west, cooler in the east.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,18,Fand warm or very warm on Thursday with
OL,19,Fsunny spells. Variable cloud with risk
OL,20,Fof a few showers on Friday. Rain
OL,21,Fspreading east on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
